%20during%20the%20week.%20But%20once%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20make%20that%20commute%2C%20we%20just%20threw%20it%20out%20there%20almost%20as%20a%20joke%3A%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20ever%20consider%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20we%20really%20do%20love%20it%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20in%20the%20woods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c52b426fcb546d2d4d9cfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFell's%20house%20in%20Pennsylvania's%20Pocono%20Mountains.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Fell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20basically%20converted%20a%20lake%20vacation%20home%20into%20a%20full-time%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20green%20grass%20and%20tall%20trees%20and%20lakes%20and%20waterfalls%20and%20fresh%20air%20%E2%80%94%20that%20just%20makes%20our%20hearts%20happy%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20seeing%20our%20kids%20have%20so%20much%20fun%20and%20enjoy%20themselves%20so%20much%20when%20they're%20outside.%20It's%20obvious%2C%20to%20me%20at%20least%2C%20that%20their%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20so%20much%20better%20growing%20up%20here%20than%20growing%20up%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20feels%20like%20this%20very%20blessed%2C%20very%20welcome%20hybrid%20%E2%80%94%20everyday%20reality%20blended%20with%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20got%20this%20little%20bubble%20of%20peace%2C%20which%2C%20again%2C%20we're%20not%20on%20vacation%2C%20we're%20just%20home.%20But%20it%20really%20does%20wonders%20for%20your%20mental%20health%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20any%20regrets.%20I%20really%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20long%20commute%20could%20lead%20to%2012-hour%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20wind%20up%20in%20Bergen%20County%20when%20they%20want%20a%20house%2C%20they%20want%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20property%2C%20but%20they%20also%20need%20that%20proximity%20to%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20a%20block%20and%20a%20half%20away%20from%20a%20bus%20stop%2C%20so%20I%20took%20the%20bus%20into%20New%20York%20City%20every%20day.%20If%20you%20got%20in%20your%20car%20and%20there%20was%20no%20traffic%2C%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20about%20a%2030-minute%20drive.%20But%20as%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20commuting%20during%20rush%20hour%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20sort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%20there%20weren't%20too%20many%20stops%20on%20the%20bus.%20But%20factoring%20in%20having%20to%20make%20some%20stops%2C%20and%20then%20the%20traffic%20each%20way%2C%20it%20was%20at%20least%20a%20little%20over%20an%20hour%20on%20the%20good%20days.%20But%20God%20forbid%20there%20was%20an%20accident%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20or%20there%20was%20bad%20weather%20like%20snow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20getting%20on%20a%20bus%20by%207%3A30%20a.m.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20to%20try%20my%20hardest%20to%20get%20on%20a%20bus%20that%20was%20leaving%20Port%20Authority%20just%20after%205%20p.m.%2C%20sometimes%20running%20from%20the%20office.%20If%20I%20didn't%20take%20that%20bus%2C%20or%20maybe%20the%20bus%20after%2C%20the%20rush-hour%20congestion%20was%20so%20bad%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20home%20until%20after%207%20p.m.%20So%20that's%20a%2012-hour%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20I%20caught%20that%20early%20bus%20and%20there%20was%20no%20traffic%2C%20I%20would%20be%20home%20by%206%3A20%20p.m.%20When%20you%20have%20young%20kids%2C%207%20p.m.%20was%20bedtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20saving%20on%20property%20taxes%20and%20were%20able%20to%20renovate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20bought%20the%20Poconos%20house%20as%20a%20vacation%20house%2C%20we%20paid%20cash%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20mortgage.%20We%20purchased%20the%20house%20for%20%24150%2C000%2C%20roughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20purchased%20the%20Midland%20Park%20house%20in%202014%20for%20about%20%24465%2C000%2C%20and%20then%20sold%20it%20in%20February%20of%202021%20for%20%24600%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20about%20New%20Jersey%20is%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20expensive.%20Taxes%20are%20quite%20high.%20I%20was%20paying%20about%20%2412%2C000%20or%20%2413%2C000%20in%20property%20taxes.%20Here%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20it's%20closer%20to%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20in%20the%20woods%20covered%20in%20snow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c52b81917a1dae02449b4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFell%20bought%20the%20Poconos%20home%20for%20%24150%2C000%20in%202020.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Fell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20out%20here%20and%20then%2C%20after%20a%20little%20while%2C%20we%20got%20pregnant%20with%20our%20second%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20needed%20to%20do%20some%20work%20to%20the%20house%20because%20the%20family%20is%20expanding.%20There's%20not%20enough%20room.%20So%20we%20did%20some%20construction%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20over%201%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20two-bedroom.%20We%20almost%20doubled%20the%20livable%20square%20footage%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20we're%20at%20somewhere%20like%201%2C800%20or%201%2C900%20square%20feet.%20Now%20it's%20three%20bedrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20get%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20very%20lucky%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20after%20I%20got%20the%20blessing%20from%20my%20boss%20to%20move%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20my%20company%20not%20only%20went%20remote%2C%20they%20got%20rid%20of%20the%20offices.%20There's%20no%20office%20to%20go%20back%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20was%20born%20in%20February%20of%202020%2C%20and%20then%20I%20was%20off%20for%20paternity%20leave%2C%20and%20then%20everybody%20just%20basically%20stayed%20home%20after%20that.%20So%20I%20haven't%20missed%20a%20beat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20a%20second%20kid%2C%20and%20I'm%20here%20for%20everything.%20It's%20so%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20working%20from%20home%2C%20you%20definitely%20have%20chores%20%E2%80%94%20you%20get%20stuff%20done%20throughout%20the%20day.%20But%20whenever%20you%20call%20it%20quits%20for%20work%2C%20you're%20already%20home.%20You%20can%20enjoy%20yourself%20or%20your%20family%20or%20whatever%20is%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20some%20people%20might%20complain%20about%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can%20imagine%20it%2C%20because%20you're%20relocating%20from%20the%20suburbs%20outside%20of%20New%20York%20City%20to%20a%20rural%20area%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20things%20are%20not%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20options%20for%20quality%20healthcare%20out%20here.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20a%20doctor%20nearby%2C%20but%20apparently%20she%20is%20one%20of%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20good%20doctors%20in%20the%20area.%20For%20my%20kids%2C%20we%20have%20to%20drive%2045%20minutes%20for%20a%20good%20pediatric%20dentist%2C%20and%2045%20minutes%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20into%20NJ%20for%20their%20pediatrician.%20People%20we've%20spoken%20to%20say%20there%20aren't%20any%20good%20hospitals%20out%20here%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20to%20NJ.%20And%20many%20people%20we%20know%20still%20travel%20all%20the%20way%20to%20NYC%20to%20see%20their%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20lived%20in%20Midland%20Park%2C%20I%20could%20literally%20walk%20out%20of%20my%20front%20door%2C%20walk%20a%20couple%20blocks%2C%20and%20be%20at%20a%20couple%20of%20neighborhood%20restaurants%2C%20a%20bar%2C%20some%20stores.%20I%20can't%20do%20that%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20instead%2C%20I%20walk%20half%20a%20block%20and%20I'm%20at%20a%20beach%20on%20a%20lake.%20So%20that's%20pretty%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20family%20loves%20the%20outdoors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%201%2C000%25%20increased%20our%20outdoor%20time.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20I%20still%20have%20to%20work%2C%20even%20though%20I'm%20working%20from%20home.%20I'm%20not%20out%20hiking%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20weather's%20nice%2C%20these%20kids%2C%20whether%20they're%20playing%20sports%2C%20or%20seeing%20friends%2C%20they're%20always%20outside.%20They're%20swimming%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20kayaking%20on%20the%20lake%2C%20and%20coming%20with%20us%20on%20hikes.%20They%20would%20much%20rather%20be%20outside%20than%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20try%20to%20go%20kayaking%20as%20often%20as%20we%20can.%20We've%20got%20a%20couple%20of%20kayaks%20and%20we%20live%20right%20on%20a%20lake%2C%20so%20it's%20like%2C%20you%20got%20it%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20just%20immersed%20ourselves%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Green%20red%2C%20and%20orange%20trees%20reflecting%20off%20of%20a%20lake.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c526f343bb77284ba5071e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20a%20lake%20from%20a%20nearby%20beach%20in%20the%20Poconos.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jason%20Fell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone's%20situations%20are%20different%20and%20everyone's%20priorities%20are%20different.%20Having%20that%20separation%20from%20the%20real%20world%20versus%20vacation%20world%20%E2%80%94%20I%20guess%20some%20people%20can%20see%20value%20in%20that.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20like%20we%20moved%20into%20our%20vacation%20home%20and%20that's%20it%20%E2%80%94%20we%20still%20go%20on%20vacation.%20We%20still%20get%20out%20to%20other%20places.%20It's%20not%20like%20we're%20stuck%20in%20this%20particular%20vacation%20land.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20if%20you%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20relocate%20or%20situate%20yourself%20somewhere%20that%20is%20going%20to%20enable%20you%20to%20pursue%20your%20professional%20career%20or%20aspirations%20while%20inspiring%20you%20and%20really%20making%20your%20heart%20happy%2C%20then%20you%20should%20really%20give%20some%20consideration%20to%20making%20that%20happen.%20If%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%2C%20financially%20and%20logistically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20either%20look%20out%20your%20window%20and%20see%20your%20neighbors%20in%20their%20aboveground%20pool%2C%2020%20feet%20away%20from%20your%20house%2C%20or%20you%20look%20outside%20and%20you%20see%20thousands%20of%20trees%20and%20the%20view%20of%20the%20lake%20through%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prefer%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20moved%20into%20your%20vacation%20home%20full-time%3F%20Business%20Insider%20wants%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%2C%20Jordan%20Pandy%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajpandy%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejpandy%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-home-primary-residence-family-benefits-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707565981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c5265c43bb77284ba506c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-home-primary-residence-family-benefits-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20vacation%20home%20in%20the%20Poconos%20became%20the%20Fell%20family's%20primary%20residence.%20They%20enjoy%20tax%20benefits%2C%20more%20family%20time%2C%20and%20being%20surrounded%20by%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvacation-home-primary-residence-family-benefits-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20gave%20identity%2C%20honoured%20transgender%20community%3A%20PM%20Modi%2