3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedell%C3%ADn%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20go%20for%20between%20%24175%2C000%20and%20%24200%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20have%20doubled%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20He%20estimates%20the%20average%20furnished%20apartment%20goes%20for%20between%20%24800%20and%20%241%2C200%20a%20month%2C%20while%20unfurnished%20apartments%20can%20cost%20as%20little%20as%20%24500%20to%20%24600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20estimates%20he%20spends%20between%20%241%2C500%20and%20%241%2C800%20a%20month%20on%20all%20his%20expenses%2C%20including%20utilities%2C%20bills%2C%20medical%20costs%2C%20dining%20out%2C%20and%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20to%20Colombia%20on%20a%20three-month%20tourist%20visa%2C%20which%20he%20extended%20for%20another%20three%20months.%20He%20applied%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cancilleria.gov.co%2Fen%2Fspecial-temporary-pensioners-visa-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epensionado%20%3C%2Fa%3Evisa%2C%20which%20is%20set%20aside%20for%20retirees%20and%20requires%20holders%20to%20earn%20about%20%24830%20in%20passive%20income%20each%20month.%20After%20living%20in%20Colombia%20for%20five%20years%20as%20a%20retiree%2C%20he%20can%20apply%20for%20permanent%20residency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20area%20is%20ideal%20for%20walking%20a%20few%20miles%20daily%20to%20keep%20healthy%2C%20given%20he%20said%20he'll%20never%20fully%20recover.%20He%20still%20has%20some%20paralysis%20and%20pain%20in%20his%20upper%20body%2C%20though%20he%20said%20the%20peacefulness%20of%20life%20has%20kept%20him%20in%20good%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20feels%20like%20a%20city%20dropped%20into%20a%20jungle%2C%26quot%3B%20Wiesmann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20weather%20was%20perfect%20for%20me%20for%20my%20disability%2C%20not%20too%20hot%20and%20not%20too%20cold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20area%20has%20many%20inexpensive%20restaurants%20and%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20to%20the%20metro%20stop%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20it's%20only%20about%2075%20cents%20per%20metro%20ride.%20Prices%20have%20shot%20up%20recently%20due%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20tourism%2C%20though%20they're%20still%20much%20cheaper%20overall%20than%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20utilities%20are%20also%20kept%20low%20because%20he%20doesn't%20use%20air%20conditioning%20or%20heating%20due%20to%20his%20area's%20temperate%20climate%2C%20with%20temperatures%20in%20the%2070s%20and%20low%2080s.%20He%20pays%20%2475%20a%20month%20for%20all%20his%20utility%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWiesmann%20said%20he%20has%20little%20intention%20of%20leaving%20Colombia%20except%20for%20vacations%20to%20see%20his%20kids%20in%20California%20and%20New%20York.%20His%20wife%20is%20Colombian%2C%20and%20he%20said%20the%20culture%20is%20very%20family-oriented%2C%20especially%20on%20Colombia's%20many%20holidays.%20There%20are%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20retirees%20and%20expats%20in%20his%20area%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20he's%20befriended.%20His%20only%20pet%20peeve%20is%20how%20people%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20felt%20at%20all%20like%20I'm%20outside%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Wiesmann%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20malls%20are%20first-rate%2C%20the%20restaurants%20are%20first-rate%20usually%2C%20the%20tap%20water%20is%20drinkable%2C%20the%20internet%20is%20fast%20and%20reliable%2C%20and%20the%20energy%20is%20fast%20and%20cheap.%20Sometimes%20I%20have%20to%20stop%20and%20say%2C%20'oh%20my%20god%2C'%20I'm%20in%20South%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20recently%20left%20the%20United%20States%20for%20a%20new%20country%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider