20of%20the%20elections%E2%80%9D.%20UK%20foreign%20secretary%20David%20Cameron%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20all%20parties%E2%80%9D%20were%20able%20to%20formally%20contest%20the%20election%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20processes%E2%80%9D%20were%20used%20to%20prevent%20some%20political%20leaders%20from%20participating.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UK%20urges%20authorities%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20uphold%20fundamental%20human%20rights%20including%20free%20access%20to%20information%2C%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cameron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20regret%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20due%20to%20the%20inability%20of%20some%20political%20actors%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%2C%20restrictions%20to%20freedom%20of%20assembly%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%20both%20online%20and%20offline%2C%20restrictions%20of%20access%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20allegations%20of%20severe%20interference%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20including%20arrests%20of%20political%20activists.%E2%80%9D%20%3Cspan%20data-contrast%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EIt%20also%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-contrast%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3Etimely%20and%20full%20investigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-contrast%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9D%20into%20all%20reported%20election%20irregularities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-ccp-props%3D%5C%22%7B%7D%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20data-contrast%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20Pakistani%20foreign%20office%20expressed%20surprise%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-contrast%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3Enegative%20tone%20of%20some%20of%20these%20statements%2C%20which%20neither%20take%20into%20account%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process%20nor%20acknowledge%20the%20free%20and%20enthusiastic%20exercise%20of%20the%20right%20to%20vote%20by%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20Pakistanis%3C%2Fspan%3E%