mg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107581848.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIran's%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20Hossein%20Amirabdollahian%2C%20expressed%20commitment%20to%20supporting%20Hezbollah%2C%20Hamas%2C%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Beirut.%20He%20praised%20Hezbollah's%20role%20in%20the%20conflict%20and%20emphasized%20Lebanon's%20security%20as%20crucial%20for%20Iran.%20Amirabdollahian%20will%20meet%20Lebanese%20officials%20and%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Nasrallah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-foreign-minister-affirms-support-for-hezbollah-amid-escalating-tensions-in-the-region%2Farticleshow%2F107581848.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-foreign-minister-affirms-support-for-hezbollah-amid-escalating-tensions-in-the-region%2Famp_articleshow%2F107581848.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firans-foreign-minister-affirms-support-for-hezbollah-amid-escalating-tensions-in-the-region%2Famp_articleshow%2F107581848.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Caste%20Census%20is%20Critical%20But%20Not%20Synonymous%20with%20Social%20Justice%3A%20Sociologist%20Satish%20Deshpande%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10155115%2FEffect-2024-02-10T155015.359.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20tool%2C%20a%20vitally%20necessary%20one%2C%20in%20the%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20a%20goal%20in%20itself%2C%20said%20eminent%20sociologist%20Satish%20Deshpande%20on%20Thursday%2C%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20delivering%20a%20lecture%20on%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%9CWill%20a%20%E2%80%98Caste%20Census%E2%80%99%20Deliver%20Social%20Justice%3F%2C%E2%80%9D%20organised%20by%20the%20Bengaluru%20Collective%20in%20association%20with%20the%20Law%20and%20Development%20Committee%20of%20the%20St.%20Joseph%E2%80%99s%20College%20of%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshpande%2C%20currently%20M.%20N.%20Srinivas%20Chair%20Professor%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Social%20and%20Economic%20Change%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%2C%E2%80%99%20more%20accurately%20termed%20a%20socio-economic%20census%2C%20is%20not%20a%20mere%20head%20count%20of%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20conducting%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%20will%20not%20lead%20us%20anywhere%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20social%20justice.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20true%20that%20if%20you%20do%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%2C%20you%20will%20necessarily%20get%20social%20justice%20out%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20asserted%20that%20it%20is%20critical%20to%20not%20conflate%20the%20concept%20of%20justice%20with%20majoritarianism%20and%20the%20morality%20that%20is%20associated%20with%20large%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshpande%20highlighted%20the%20dual%20challenge%20of%20addressing%20the%20needs%20of%20smaller%20or%20numerically%20minor%20castes%20from%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20without%20losing%20sight%20of%20the%20broader%20goal%20of%20social%20justice.%20The%20lecture%20delved%20into%20the%20historical%20context%2C%20the%20contemporary%20relevance%20of%20caste%20data%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20of%20such%20data%20to%20influence%20social%20and%20political%20dynamics.%20Deshpande%20raised%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20representation%20and%20treatment%20of%20minority%20castes%2C%20the%20complexities%20of%20political%20mobilisation%20around%20caste%20identities%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20implications%20for%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshpande%20emphasised%20that%20publicly%20available%20socio-economic%20census%20data%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20transformative%20%E2%80%9Cawareness%20of%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20could%20generate%20a%20social%20force%20in%20its%20own%20right%2C%20potentially%20reshaping%20the%20political%20and%20social%20landscapes.%20Crucially%2C%20however%2C%20this%20force%20is%20but%20of%20tangential%20relevance%20to%20social%20justice%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%20Drawing%20from%20historical%20precedents%20and%20recent%20developments%2C%20he%20unpacked%20the%20layered%20dynamics%20between%20caste%20enumeration%2C%20social%20justice%20policies%2C%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20majority%20versus.%20minority%20statuses%20within%20Indian%20society.%20The%20professor%20discussed%20the%20difference%20between%20knowing%20the%20numbers%20in%20an%20arithmetic%20sense%20and%20knowing%20it%20in%20a%20political%20sense%2C%20and%20the%20role%20of%20mechanisms%20like%20a%20census%20in%20crystallising%20identities%20and%20generating%20political%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshpande%20argued%20against%20the%20tendency%20to%20conflate%20the%20notion%20of%20social%20justice%20with%20empirical%20data%20or%20evidence%20alone%2C%20and%20urged%20citizens%20to%20be%20mindful%20so%20that%20they%20do%20not%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20numbers.%20Illustratively%2C%20he%20spoke%20of%20the%20necessity%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20potential%20risks%20for%20the%20smaller%20castes%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20social%20spectrum%2C%20in%20the%20grand%20calculus%20of%20social%20justice%E2%80%94how%20they%20might%20fare%20when%20the%20numbers%20reveal%20the%20realities%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmajority%E2%80%9D%20versus%20%E2%80%9Cminority%E2%80%9D.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20many%2Ffew%20and%20good%2Fless-good%20are%20socially%20constructed%2C%20not%20naturally%20occurring%20in%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20we%20afford%20to%20have%20the%20claims%20of%20certain%20caste%20groups%20to%20be%20toned%20down%20in%20some%20way%20merely%20because%20they%20are%20smaller%20in%20number%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Prof.%20Deshpande.%20This%20is%20of%20particular%20importance%20in%20the%20current%20political%20climate%2C%20he%20argued%2C%20where%20there%20is%20no%20room%20to%20speak%20of%20minority%20rights.%20Yet%2C%20he%20made%20his%20conviction%20unmistakably%20clear%20by%20asserting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20doing%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%20will%20certainly%20not%20lead%20us%20in%20the%20direction%20towards%20social%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lecture%20was%20a%20call%20to%20look%20deeper%2C%20an%20invitation%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthink%20about%20the%20associations%20we%20make%2C%20political%20and%20moral%2C%20between%20many-ness%20and%20few-ness%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20census%20is%20primarily%20a%20device%20to%20identify%20many-ness%20and%20few-ness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20professor%20expressed%20his%20concerns%20on%20whether%20merely%20recognising%20the%20numerical%20strength%20or%20weakness%20of%20certain%20castes%20could%20lead%20to%20reparative%20justice%2C%20or%20result%20in%20risking%20further%20reinforcement%20of%20existing%20prejudices.%20Responding%20to%20questions%20on%20why%20the%20headcount%20alone%20may%20not%20produce%20change%2C%20Deshpande%20said%20the%20audience%20to%20not%20forget%20that%20justice%20and%20injustice%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20numbers%20alone.%20He%20argued%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20social%20justice%20does%20not%20come%20from%20belonging%20to%20any%20particular%20caste%2C%20but%20from%20the%20social%20reality%20that%20persons%20belonging%20to%20a%20particular%20caste%20are%20treated%20in%20a%20particular%20unjust%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20tension%20between%20economic%20status-based%20reservations%20(EWS)%20and%20caste-based%20reservations%2C%20Prof%20Deshpande%20reiterated%20the%20distinct%20nature%20of%20caste%20injustice%20that%20cannot%20be%20equated%20with%20economic%20disadvantage%20alone%2C%20emphasising%20the%20need%20for%20caste-sensitive%20policies.%20The%20nature%20of%20caste%20politics%20under%20Hindutva%20was%20discussed%20as%20well.%20Regarding%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20broader%20Hindutva%20umbrella%20under%20which%20caste%20would%20ceases%20to%20matter%2C%20Deshpande%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CCaste%20will%20not%20be%20defeated%20by%20Hindutva%2C%20given%20that%20it%20has%20been%20around%20for%20a%20few%20thousand%20years%20more%20than%20the%20Hindu%20identity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Awanish%20Kumar%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20faculty%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Development%2C%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%C2%A0%20who%20chaired%20the%20event%2C%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98caste%20census%E2%80%99%20in%20India.%20He%20questioned%20its%20terminology%2C%20highlighting%20its%20historical%20roots%20and%20current%20relevance%2C%20notably%20through%20early%2020th-century%20efforts%20and%20recent%20Bihar%20survey%20findings.%20He%20underscored%20the%20importance%20of%20such%20data%20for%20understanding%20societal%20structures%20and%20for%20formulating%20development%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%E2%80%99s%20discussions%20illuminated%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20socio-economic%20census%20data%20in%20crafting%20informed%20social%20policies%2C%20while%20acknowledging%20the%20challenges%20and%20limitations%20inherent%20in%20using%20it%20alone%20to%20address%20India%E2%80%99s%20deep-rooted%20social%20inequalities.%20This%20dialogue%20underscored%20the%20ongoing%20need%20for%20a%20thoughtful%20engagement%20with%20caste%20dynamics%2C%20social%20justice%2C%20and%20the%20pursuit%20of%20equitable%20solutions%20in%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20diverse%20societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESethu%20and%20Sai%20Chandan%20are%20researchers%20at%20the%20Foundation%20for%20Agrarian%20Studies%2C%20Bengaluru.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707561053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10155115%2FEffect-2024-02-10T155015.359.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcaste-census-is-critical-but-not-synonymous-with-social-justice-sociologist-satish-deshpande%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20a%20lecture%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20eminent%20sociologist%20raised%20critical%20questions%20about%20representation%20and%20treatment%20of%20minority%20castes%2C%20complexities%20of%20political%20mobilisation%20around%20caste%20identities%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20implications%20for%20social%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcaste-census-is-critical-but-not-synonymous-with-social-justice-sociologist-satish-deshpande%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20asks%20FIFA%20to%20ban%20Israel%20over%20ongoing%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707561014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107581773%2Cimgsize-1347862.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Firan-asks-fifa-to-ban-israel-over-ongoing-war-against-hamas-in-gaza%2Farticleshow%2F107581567.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107581567.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIran's%20football%20federation%20has%20called%20on%20FIFA%20to%20suspend%20Israel's%20football%20federation%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20its%20website%2C%20the%20Iranian%20football%20federation%20has%20urged%20FIFA%20to%20completely%20halt%20all%20f