nion%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmoment%20of%20pride%26quot%3B%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20former%20PM%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpiyush-goyal-vice-president-criticizes-congress-for-ignoring-charan-singh-demands-apology%2Farticleshow%2F107579810.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20Week%20for%20the%20Next%20Two%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F11152259%2FIMG_0081.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%20Although%20it%20may%20appear%20closer%20to%20reality%20than%20fiction.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20committee%20for%20success%20(CCS)%E2%80%94a%20high-level%2C%20influential%20monitoring%20body%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20prime%20minister%2C%20met%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFebruary%2010%20in%20a%20regular%20session%2C%20a%20monthly%20ritual%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20changing%20political%20landscape.%20As%20per%20the%20protocol%2C%20the%20meeting%20was%20off%20the%20books%20%E2%80%93%20no%20record%2C%20no%20notes%2C%20no%20information%2C%20and%20of%20course%20no%20PIB%20press%20release%3B%20not%20even%2C%20an%20ANI%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20admiration%20and%20awe%20at%20the%20way%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20moved%20on%20various%20fronts%20with%20dexterity%20and%20panache.%20While%20there%20was%20no%20particular%20jubilation%20over%20his%20two%20recent%20parliamentary%20performances%20%5Broutine%20and%20predictable%2C%20as%20one%20participant%20muttered%20inaudibly%5D%2C%20there%20was%20positive%20excitement%20over%20the%20imaginative%20use%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20made%20of%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20awards%20to%20garner%20a%20few%2C%20petty%20political%20advantages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Boss%20proxy%20revealed%20the%20thinking%20at%20the%20highest%20level%3A%20let%20editorial%20writers%20vent%20their%20disapproval%20at%20this%20%E2%80%9Ccheapening%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20award%20but%20anything%20and%20everything%20that%20helps%20in%20getting%20over%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20majority%20line%20will%20be%20pursued.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20can%20paraphrase%20the%20boss%E2%80%99s%20thought%20process%2C%20it%20goes%20like%20this%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20bothered%20with%20constitutional%20protocols%2C%20sanctity%20of%20traditions%20and%20all%20that%20%3Cem%3Ebakwas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rubbish)%20the%20Khan%20Market%20gang%20keep%20talking%20about%3B%20we%20have%20the%20will%20to%20prevail%20and%C2%A0%20shall%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20a%20third%20term.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20participants%20were%20suitably%20impressed%20at%20this%20brutal%20clarity%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%C2%A0%20They%20were%20further%20impressed%20that%20the%20Big%20Boss%20has%2C%20up%20its%20sleeve%2C%20a%20few%20more%20Bharat%20Ratna%20announcements%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJayalalitha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20To%20blunt%20the%20allegation%20of%20being%20anti-South%2C%20as%20also%20to%20entice%20the%20wobbly%20and%20confused%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20voter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBalasaheb%20Thackrey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20This%20will%20be%20the%20last%20nail%20the%20coffin%20of%20the%20Udhav%20Thackrey%20faction.%20The%20entire%20Sharad%20Pawar-alliance%20will%20collapse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDevraj%20Urs%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20final%20appropriation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98social%20justice%E2%80%99%20plank.%20Karnataka%20will%20be%20in%20the%20pocket.%20Siddaramaiah%20can%20come%20to%20Delhi%20and%20do%20his%20%3Cem%3Etamasha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20we%20shall%20be%20eloping%20with%20the%20tallest%20Kannadiga%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-secret-report-lauds-the-indian-media%5C%22%3EA%20Secret%20Report%20Lauds%20the%20Indian%20Media%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20Not%20only%20would%20it%20be%20reminder%20to%20the%20BJP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekaryakarta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20did%20not%20give%20the%20founder%20of%20our%20party%20the%20highest%20honour%2C%20it%20will%20also%20endear%20us%20to%20the%20bhadralok%20constituency%20which%20still%20remains%20loyal%20to%20Mamta%20Banerjee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBiju%20Patnaik%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20shall%20be%20able%20to%20knock%20off%20Navin%20Patnaik%20from%20his%20smug%20love%20affair%20with%20the%20Oriya%20voter.%20We%20shall%20steal%20the%20father%20from%20the%20son%20and%20many%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20Orissa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20was%20given%20to%20understand%20that%20no%20one%20should%20be%20surprised%20if%20one%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20week%20was%20announced%20before%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20comes%20into%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20many%20CCS%20members%20were%20curious%20to%20know%20why%20so%20much%20trouble%20is%20being%20taken%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%20more%20than%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Boss%20Proxy%3A%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20where%20nobody%20has%20ever%20been%20able%20to%20de-code%20the%20sheer%20street-smartness%20of%20the%20Boss%E2%80%99%20grand%20strategy.%20You%20create%20this%20massive%20perception%2C%20with%20those%20silly%20Pavlovian%20dogs%20in%20the%20media%20echoing%20the%20inevitability%20of%20a%20Modi%20wave.%20They%20fall%20over%20one%20another%20in%20serenading%20this%20or%20that%20master-stroke%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20They%20openly%20permit%20themselves%20to%20say%20how%20clever%20and%20brilliant%20our%20man%20is%3B%20and%2C%20by%20the%20same%20token%2C%20they%20have%20good%20reason%20to%20find%20the%20opposition%20in%20a%20disarray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%20is%20the%20secret%20%5Bnot%20to%20be%20whispered%20outside%20this%20room%5D%3A%20once%20the%20overwhelming%20perception%20of%20an%20unstoppable%20Modi%20wave%20gets%20cast%20in%20stone%2C%20then%20we%20have%20practically%20fixed%20the%20%E2%80%98mood%20of%20the%20nation.%E2%80%99%20And%20then%20nobody%20will%20want%20to%20call%20out%20our%20%E2%80%9Cmisuse%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20system%20%5Bwith%20due%20apologies%20to%20Justice%20Sinha%2C%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20case%20fame%5D.%20Even%20the%20courts%20will%20look%20the%20other%20way%2C%20what%20to%20talk%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20My%20own%20gut%20feeling%20is%20that%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C370%E2%80%9D%20declaration%2C%20this%20business%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20judicial%20back-burner%20or%20even%20be%20decided%20in%20our%20favour.%20It%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20power%20jungle%20that%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20take%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanga%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20sure%20%E2%80%98winner%E2%80%99.%20And%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%20will%20be%20that%20the%20media%20will%20pat%20itself%20on%20the%20back%20for%20being%20so%20precise%20and%20accurate%20in%20predicting%20a%20Modi%20wave.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20was%20once%20again%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20unending%20tricks%20the%20Big%20Boss%20has%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20They%20all%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20that%20he%20should%20give%20himself%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20is%20the%20pen-name%20of%20an%20aspiring%20satirist%2C%20who%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Vishwavguru%20Archives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20believes%20that%20ridicule%20and%20humour%20are%20central%20to%20freedom%20to%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707555730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F11152259%2FIMG_0081.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-bharat-ratna-a-week-for-the-next-two-months%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20Vishwaguru%20Archives%3A%20Let%20editorial%20writers%20vent%20their%20disapproval%20at%20this%20%E2%80%9Ccheapening%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20award%2C%20there%20is%20positive%20excitement%20over%20the%20imaginative%20use%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20made%20of%20the%C2%A0Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20garner%20a%20few%2C%20petty%20political%20advantages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-bharat-ratna-a-week-for-the-next-two-months%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20Week%20for%20the%20Next%20Two%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F11152259%2FIMG_0081.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20work%20of%20fiction.%20Although%20it%20m