ve%20culture%20and%20to%20convert%20Hindus%20to%20Christianity%2C%20the%20UCA%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20Christians%20make%20up%203.74%20percent%20of%20the%20population%2C%20exceeding%20the%20national%20average%20of%202.3%20percent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20(UCF)%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%20focused%20on%20Christian%20issues%2C%20had%20released%20a%20statement%20last%20year%20highlighting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3Ethe%20rise%20in%20attacks%20against%20the%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3E525%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%202023.%20The%20group%20had%20cautioned%20that%20if%20the%20trend%20were%20to%20continue%20then%202023%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20violent%20and%20difficult%20years%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20India%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%20breaking%20the%20recent%20record%20set%20by%202022%2C%20and%202021%20before%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20incidents%20of%20violence%20are%20by%20mob%20violence%20led%20by%20so%20called%20vigilante%20groups%20of%20particular%20faith%20who%20are%20allegedly%20receiving%20support%20from%20people%20in%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20organisation%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707553720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20233349%2FIMG_0509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fassam-hindu-group-threatens-ch