st%20seats%20by%20a%20single%20party%20in%20Thursday's%20election%2C%20but%20supporters%20of%20imprisoned%20Khan%2C%20who%20ran%20as%20independents%20instead%20of%20as%20a%20single%20bloc%20after%20his%20party%20was%20barred%20from%20the%20polls%2C%20won%20the%20most%20seats%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20said%20his%20party%20would%20talk%20to%20other%20groups%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government%20as%20it%20had%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20clear%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif's%20announcement%20came%20after%20more%20than%20three-quarters%20of%20the%20265%20seats%20had%20declared%20results%2C%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20polling%20ended%20on%20Thursday%20when%2028%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20militant%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20had%20predicted%20there%20may%20be%20no%20clear%20winner%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20woes%20of%20a%20country%20struggling%20to%20recover%20from%20an%20economic%20crisis%20while%20it%20grapples%20with%20rising%20militancy%20in%20a%20deeply%20polarised%20political%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20independents%2C%20most%20of%20them%20backed%20by%20Khan%2C%20had%20won%20the%20most%20seats%20-%2098%20of%20the%20245%20counted%20by%201830%20GMT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif's%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20won%2069%20while%20the%20Pakistan%20People's%20Party%20of%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20the%20son%20of%20assassinated%20premier%20Benazir%20Bhutto%2C%20got%2051.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20were%20won%20by%20small%20parties%20and%20other%20independents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20Muslim%20League%20is%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20the%20country%20today%20after%20the%20elections%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20bring%20this%20country%20out%20of%20the%20whirlpool%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharif%20told%20a%20crowd%20of%20supporters%20gathered%20outside%20his%20home%20in%20the%20eastern%20city%20of%20Lahore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20has%20got%20the%20mandate%2C%20whether%20independents%20or%20parties%2C%20we%20respect%20the%20mandate%20they%20have%20got%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20invite%20them%20to%20sit%20with%20us%20and%20help%20this%20wounded%20nation%20get%20back%20on%20its%20feet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20released%20an%20audio-visual%20message%20created%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20shared%20on%20his%20X%20social%20media%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20message%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20delivered%20by%20word%20through%20his%20lawyers%2C%20Khan%2C%2071%2C%20rejected%20Sharif's%20claim%20to%20victory%2C%20congratulated%20his%20supporters%20on%20%26quot%3Bwinning%26quot%3B%20the%20election%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20celebrate%20and%20protect%20their%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20trusted%20that%20you%20all%20would%20come%20out%20to%20vote%20-%20and%20you%20honoured%20that%20trust%20and%20your%20massive%20turnout%20has%20shocked%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20said%2C%20adding%20no%20one%20would%20accept%20Sharif's%20claim%20because%20he%20had%20won%20fewer%20seats%20and%20because%20there%20had%20been%20rigging%20in%20the%20polls.Former%20cricket%20superstar%20Khan%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20August%2C%20and%20was%20convicted%20three%20times%20in%20six%20days%20in%20the%20leadup%20to%20the%20polls%20for%2010%2C%2014%20and%20seven%20years%20in%20cases%20related%20to%20state%20secrets%2C%20graft%20and%20an%20unlawful%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%2C%2074%2C%20a%20three-time%20former%20premier%2C%20returned%20from%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20late%20last%20year%2C%20having%20contested%20the%20last%20election%20from%20a%20jail%20cell%20on%20a%20graft%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20considered%20the%20front-runner%20to%20lead%20the%20country%2C%20having%20buried%20a%20long-running%20feud%20with%20the%20powerful%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20said%20his%20party%20would%20have%20preferred%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20that%20would%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20others%2C%20including%20former%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20of%20PPP%2C%20to%20open%20negotiations%20as%20early%20as%20Friday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20reaction%2C%20a%20senior%20aide%20of%20Khan%20said%20PTI%20leaders%20would%20hold%20talks%20among%20themselves%20and%20also%20meet%20Khan%20in%20jail%20on%20Saturday%20to%20discuss%20the%20results%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResults%20of%20the%20vote%20have%20been%20unusually%20delayed%2C%20which%20the%20caretaker%20government%20ascribed%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20phone%20services%20-%20a%20security%20measure%20ahead%20of%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20members%20cannot%20form%20a%20government%20on%20their%20own%20under%20Pakistan's%20complex%20election%20system%20which%20also%20includes%20reserved%20seats%20that%20will%20be%20allotted%20to%20parties%20based%20on%20their%20winnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20independents%20have%20the%20option%20to%20join%20any%20party%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20For%20Coalition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20timely%20announcement%20of%20the%20results%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20smooth%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20government%2C%20will%20reduce%20policy%20and%20political%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody's%20Investors%20Service%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20country%20that%20is%20facing%20very%20challenging%20macroeconomic%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20the%20announcement%20of%20results%20was%20unusual%20for%20Pakistan.%20Karachi's%20stock%20index%20and%20Pakistan's%20sovereign%20bonds%20fell%20because%20of%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20electoral%20battle%20had%20been%20expected%20to%20be%20between%20candidates%20backed%20by%20Khan%2C%20whose%20PTI%20won%20the%20last%20national%20election%2C%20and%20the%20PML-N.%20Khan%20believes%20the%20powerful%20military%20is%20behind%20a%20crackdown%20to%20hound%20his%20party%20out%20of%20existence%2C%20while%20analysts%20and%20opponents%20say%20Sharif%20is%20being%20backed%20by%20the%20generals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20has%20dominated%20the%20nuclear-armed%20country%20either%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20in%20its%2076%20years%20of%20independence%20from%20Britain%20but%20for%20several%20years%20it%20has%20maintained%20it%20does%20not%20interfere%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20a%20coalition%20government%20will%20struggle%20to%20tackle%20multiple%20challenges%20-%20foremost%20being%20seeking%20a%20new%20bailout%20programme%20from%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20after%20the%20current%20arrangement%20expires%20in%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coalition%20government%20%26quot%3Bwould%20probably%20be%20unstable%2C%20weak%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20big%20loser%20...%20will%20be%20the%20army%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Marvin%20Weinbaum%2C%20Director%20of%20Afghanistan%20and%20Pakistan%20Studies%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20army%20really%20has%20staked%20its%20reputation%20on%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver%20this%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%20expected%20to%20help%20resolve%20the%20crises%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20but%20a%20fractured%20verdict%20%26quot%3Bcould%20very%20well%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20even%20deeper%20exposure%20to%20forces%20which%20would%20create%20instability%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1