Ein%20the%20Lower%20House%20on%20Thursday%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20Congress%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-failures%5C%22%3Eblack%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%2C%20says%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20inherited%20an%20economy%20that%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20fragile%20state%3B%20public%20finances%20were%20in%20bad%20shape%3B%20there%20was%20economic%20mismanagement%20and%20financial%20indiscipline%3B%20and%20there%20was%20widespread%20corruption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20reply%20to%20the%20Lower%20House%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20discussion%2C%20union%20minister%20of%20finance%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20responding%20to%20arguments%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20who%20called%20the%20document%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20said%20that%20the%20paper%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20document%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20prime%20minister%20Modi%20in%202016%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20it%20was%20decided%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20economy%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20suggestions%20coming%20up%20that%20I%20should%20lay%20a%20White%20Paper%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20economy.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20doing%20it%20because%20of%20national%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20quoted%20Modi%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20if%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%20would%20have%20come%20out%20then%2C%20not%20a%20single%20investor%20would%20have%20come%20and%20our%20own%20citizens%20would%20have%20asked%20what%20was%20going%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20said%20that%20during%20the%20UPA%20years%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20ticket%20corruption%20was%20one%20a%20year%2C%20so%20our%20own%20citizens%20would%20have%20lost%20confidence%20in%20the%20economy%20because%20of%20the%20white%20paper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%2010%20years%20which%20can%20be%20periodically%20compared%20to%20UPA%E2%80%99s%2010%20years.%20Responsibly%2C%20we%20took%20the%20challenge%20of%20getting%20everything%20sorted%20out.%20Now%2C%20having%20placed%20the%20economy%20in%20a%20better%20position%2C%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20the%20white%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20the%20opposition%2C%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20the%20document%20is%20based%20on%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20challenge%20anyone%20who%20says%20this%20document%20is%20baseless.%20Everything%20is%20with%20evidence.%20I%20challenge%20anyone%20who%20says%20that%20we%20have%20kept%20the%20White%20Paper%20which%20has%20no%20proof%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Concoction%20of%20lies%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20MPs%20during%20their%20speeches%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20white%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremachandran%2C%20who%20had%20also%20moved%20a%20motion%20disapproving%20it%2C%20said%20during%20his%20speech%20that%20the%20white%20paper%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20attempt%20to%20ignore%20the%20valuable%20efforts%20of%20the%20previous%20UPA%20government%20and%20the%20contributions%20of%20renowned%20economists%20and%20scientists%20and%20experts%20from%202004%20to%202014.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20growth%20of%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20price%20rise%20and%20increase%20in%20poverty%20and%20%E2%80%9Cshifting%20the%20blame%20on%20to%20the%20previous%20government%20for%20failures%20of%20this%20government%20is%20not%20proper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20Roy%20who%20had%20moved%20the%20second%20motion%20disapproving%20the%20white%20paper%20said%20that%20the%20the%20finance%20minister%20should%20have%20first%20apoligised%20to%20the%20nation%20for%20demonetisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20not%20been%20a%20bigger%20scam%20in%20the%20history%20of%20this%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20pointing%20to%20the%20cash%20in%20circulation%20returning%20to%20the%20economy%20after%20the%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERay%20also%20demanded%20to%20know%20what%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20extradite%20fugitive%20economic%20offenders%20like%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20Mehul%20Choksi%20and%20Vijay%20Mallya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20poorest%20among%20BRICS%20nations.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20India%20grow%20as%20per%20its%20potential%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20behind%20China%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20little%20growth%20in%20jobs%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20Roy%20said%20only%20%E2%80%9Ca%20few%20well%20connected%20families%20have%20accounted%20for%20significant%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGovernment%20has%20no%20answers%20on%20unemployment%2C%20demonetisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%20said%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20white%20paper%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Celection%20manifesto%E2%80%9D%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20UPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20intent%20and%20purpose%20of%20bringing%20this%20kind%20of%20White%20Paper%20simply%20is%20not%20convincing.%20It%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20sheer%20concoction%2C%20rather%20a%20granary%20of%20concoctions%20and%20mountain%20of%20lies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20the%20session%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20white%20paper%20only%20with%20the%20objective%20to%20tarnish%20the%20ten%20years%20of%20UPA%20government%2C%20does%20not%20cut%20ice.%20It%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20electoral%20manifesto%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20scoring%20electoral%20brownie%20points%20that%20has%20prompted%20you%20to%20bring%20this%20kind%20of%20white%20paper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20demanded%20to%20know%20from%20the%20finance%20minister%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20declining%20GDP%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGDP%20growth%20during%20UPA%20was%206.8%25%20on%20average%2C%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20it%20is%205.9%25%20on%20average%2C%20tell%20us%20is%20China%20responsible%20or%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Chiding%20data%E2%80%9D%20Owaisi%20asked%20why%20Unemployment%20Survey%20done%20since%202011%20and%20the%20PLF%20survey%20(National%20Survey%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey)%20and%20consumption%20survey%20that%20happened%20in%202018%20and%202017%20respectively%20have%20not%20been%20done%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20said%20that%20while%20a%20white%20paper%20usually%20covers%20an%20issue%20in-depth%2C%20and%20ways%20to%20resolve%20a%20problem%2C%20the%20white%20paper%20brought%20by%20the%20government%20only%20included%20%E2%80%9Callegations%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20previous%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20white%20paper%2C%20it%20is%20a%20politically%20coloured%20paper%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20MP%20DNV%20Senthilkumar%20S%20called%20the%20white%20paper%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwolf%20in%20sheep%E2%80%99s%20clothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20white%20paper%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20concoction%20of%20twisted%20facts%20and%20selective%20memory%20conveniently%20ignoring%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20present%20administration.%20The%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20blaming%20the%20Congress%20and%20Nehru%20for%20everything.%20They%20have%20been%20in%20power%20for%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20and%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20merits%20and%20their%20success%20but%20they%20still%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20Congress%20and%20Nehru%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%2C%20jobs%20and%20leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20in%20her%20reply%20said%20that%20under%20the%20UPA%20average%20annual%20inflation%20was%208.2%25%2C%20and%20that%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20it%20has%20averaged%209.8%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20UPA%2C%20retail%20inflation%20was%20more%20than%209%25%20for%2022%20months%2C%20our%20retail%20inflation%20was%20mostly%20at%205%25%2C%20never%20crossed%208%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20Modi%20years%2C%20unemployment%20has%20recorded%20a%20decrease%20from%205.8%25%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%203.2%25%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg%20that%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funemployment-rate-rose-to-10-09-percent-in-october-cmie-data%5C%22%3ECentre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20rose%20to%20a%20two-year%20high%20of%2010.09%25%20in%20October%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20over%208%20lakh%20central%20government%20vacancies%20had%20been%20filled%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20transparency%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20gig%20economy%20had%20created%2077%20lakh%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Santosh%20Mehrotra%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-we-know-about-indias-post-covid-economy-recovery-and-rising-inequality%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20open%20unemployment%20was%20barely%202.1%25%20in%202012%20(the%20last%20year%20for%20which%20data%20was%20available%20before%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power)%20and%20had%20already%20nearly%20tripled%20to%206.1%25%20in%202018%20(National%20Survey%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%2C%20conducted%20annually%20since%202017-18)%2C%20the%20highest%20rate%20in%2045%20years%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20also%20accused%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20of%20wanting%20credit%20for%20schemes%20like%20MGNREGA%2C%20DBT%20and%20Aadhaar%20but%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CUIDAI%E2%80%99s%20parent%20body%20in%20UPA%2C%20the%20Planning%20Commission%2C%20was%20rejecting%20its%20proposal%20of%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20three%20ministries%20at%20that%20time%20had%20serious%20reservations%20with%20real-time%20bio-metric%20authentication%20but%20Congress%20still%20says%20that%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar%20is%20ours.%E2%80%99%20It%20was%20said%20that%20UIDAI%20was%20%E2%80%98conceptualised%20with%20no%20clarity%20of%20purpose%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20it%20was%20due%20to%20Aadhaar%20%26amp%3B%20DBT%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20able%20to%20send%20money%20directly%20into%20beneficiaries%E2%80%99%20accounts%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20leadership%20and%20vision%20which%20the%20UPA%20completely%20lacked%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20embracing%20Aadhaar%2C%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20including%20Modi%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Faadhaar-gets-a-second-life-from-modi-114102800024_1.html%5C%22%3Erallied%20against%20Aadhaar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20criticised%20the%20biometric%20identity%20card%20as%20a%20waste%20of%20taxpayers%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707499157000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F24160818%2FScreenshot-2023-03-24-at-4.07.15-PM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthe