o-report-124020901434_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhyundai-motor-picks-jpmorgan-citi-to-accelerate-3-billion-ipo-report-124020901434_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChose%20Rashtraneeti%20Over%20Rajneeti%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20On%20Why%20White%20Paper%20Was%20Brought%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20said%20his%20government%20could%20have%20brought%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20economy%20in%202014%20itself%20when%20it%20came%20to%20power%20but%20he%20chose%20'rashtraneeti'%20over%20'rajneeti'%20as%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20shake%20the%20country's%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20has%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20last%20Parliament%20session%20before%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi-led%20government%20on%20Thursday%20brought%20a%20white%20paper%20tearing%20into%20Congress-led%20UPA%20rule%20and%20saying%20that%20it%20had%20turned%20the%20Indian%20economy%20into%20a%20non-performing%20one%20through%20indiscriminate%20revenue%20expenditure%2C%20off%20budget%20borrowings%20and%20pile%20of%20bad%20debts%20at%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20Times%20Groups'%20ET%20NOW%20Global%20Business%20Summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20in%20the%20decade%20before%202014%2C%20the%20policies%20on%20which%20the%20country%20was%20running%20was%20taking%20the%20country%20on%20the%20path%20of%20bankruptcy.%20%26quot%3BOn%20this%2C%20we%20have%20tabled%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20economy%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20discussion%20on%20it%20is%20ongoing.%20Since%20there%20is%20such%20a%20big%20audience%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20state%20my%20'Mann%20ki%20Baat'%20also%20that%20the%20white%20paper%20that%20I%20have%20brought%20now%2C%20I%20could%20have%20brought%20in%202014.%20If%20my%20aim%20had%20been%20to%20derive%20political%20gain%2C%20then%20I%20would%20have%20kept%20those%20figures%20before%20the%20people%2010%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20things%20came%20before%20me%20in%202014%2C%20I%20was%20stunned.%20The%20economy%20was%20in%20a%20critical%20situation.%20Due%20to%20scams%20and%20policy%20paralysis%2C%20there%20was%20widespread%20pessimism%20among%20global%20investors.%20If%20I%20would%20have%20brought%20these%20things%20to%20light%2C%20if%20a%20wrong%20signal%20would%20have%20gone%2C%20probably%20the%20country%20would%20have%20lost%20its%20confidence%20in%20the%20country%20like%20when%20a%20patient%20gets%20to%20know%20that%20he%20has%20a%20serious%20disease%2C%20he%20panics%2C%20and%20the%20country%20would%20have%20felt%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20bringing%20the%20white%20paper%20in%202014%20would%20have%20suited%20him%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Rajniti'%20tells%20me%20to%20do%20that%20but%20'Rashtraneeti'%20does%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20do%20that%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20I%20chose%20'rashtraneeti'%20over%20'rajneeti'.%20And%20when%20the%20situation%20has%20become%20strong%20in%2010%20years%20and%20we%20can%20sustain%20any%20assault%2C%20then%20I%20thought%20I%20should%20tell%20the%20truth%20to%20the%20people%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20released%20white%20paper%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20it%2C%20you%20will%20know%20where%20we%20were%20and%20from%20what%20situation%20we%20have%20risen%20and%20reached%20here.%20Now%20you%20are%20seeing%20the%20new%20height%20of%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20it%20is%20his%20guarantee%20that%20in%20his%20third%20term%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20world's%20third%20largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20Times%20Group%20MD%20Vineet%20Jain%20said%20the%20last%20ten%20years%C2%A0have%20been%20transformative%20for%20India%20with%20its%20economy%20undergoing%20significant%20structural%20reforms%2C%20boosting%20its%20macroeconomic%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20embark%20on%20'Amritkaal'%2C%20I%20want%20us%20all%20to%20envision%20a%20futuristic%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20prosperous%20society%20rooted%20in%20a%20human-centric%20approach.%20This%20will%20be%20our%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20two%20decades%20belong%20to%20India%2C%20where%20initiatives%20like%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20Create%20in%20India%2C%20Serve%20from%20India%2C%20and%20Start%20up%20India%20converge%20into%20a%20majestic%20narrative%2C%20transforming%20the%20nation%20into%20a%20knowledge%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20vision%20aligns%20perfectly%20with%20the%20theme%20of%20this%20year's%20ET%20Now%20Global%20Business%20Summit%20-%20Disruption%2C%20Development%2C%20Diversification%20-%20an%20intricate%20tale%20echoing%20your%20vision%20to%20craft%20India%20as%20the%20Vishwaguru.%20During%20this%20time%20of%20change%2C%20there%20is%20no%20better%20guide%20than%20you%2C%20prime%20minister%2C%20to%20set%20the%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707498540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fg6c34tl8_pm-modi-pti_625x300_09_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-on-why-white-paper-was-brought-now-chose-rashtraneeti-over-rajneeti-5027248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20said%20his%20government%20could%20have%20brought%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20economy%20in%202014%20its