20an%20Olympic%20medal%2C%20will%20we%20see%20them%20as%20a%20child%20from%20Jharkhand%20or%20from%20India%3F%20What%20are%20we%20saying%3F%20What%20language%20is%20being%20used%3F%20Can%20we%20say%20that%20vaccines%20were%20made%20in%20one%20corner%20so%20cannot%20be%20used%20by%20others%20in%20the%20country%3F%20Such%20a%20mindset%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20national%20party.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20tax%2C%20our%20money!%20What%20language%20is%20being%20used%3F%20This%20is%20dangerous%20to%20the%20future%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Modi%20as%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20before%202014%20had%20been%20the%20most%20vocal%20proponent%20of%20a%20fair%20devolution%20of%20taxes%2C%20and%20frequently%20attacked%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance-led%20Centre%20for%20denying%20Gujarat%20its%20fiscal%20rights%20%E2%80%93%20precisely%20what%20chief%20ministers%20like%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Y.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20or%20M.K.Stalin%20are%20currently%20saying.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20look%20at%20a%20few%20instances%20where%20Modi%20had%20publicly%20registered%20his%20dissent%20over%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20low%20share%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202008%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20collects%20around%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore%20as%20its%20contribution%20to%20the%20total%20tax%20revenue%20of%20the%20country%20but%20gets%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmeasly%202.5%25%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20central%20funds.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Centre%20so%20wishes%2C%20it%20need%20not%20pay%20anything%20to%20Gujarat%20for%20a%20year%20but%20then%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20also%20not%20collect%20any%20taxes%20from%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fmodi-kicks-up-a-storm-with-no-tax-remark%2Fstory-opGd2Pd4OC0lPApoJDv3DJ_amp.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20years%20later%2C%20on%20January%209%2C%202012%2C%20he%20said%20at%20the%2010th%20Pravasi%20Bharatiya%20Divas%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20get%20(something)%20from%20the%20Centre%20or%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20We%20have%20to%20do%20everything%20on%20our%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20(Ashok%20Ghelot)%20said%20he%20has%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20central%20government%20and%20the%20prime%20minister.%20But%20we%20are%20not%20fortunate%20enough.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20anything.%20We%20have%20to%20do%20everything%20on%20our%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rediff.com%2Fnews%2Fslide-show%2Fslide-show-1-at-pbd-modi-dumps-his-speech-says-oppn-ruled-states-neglected%2F20120109.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20said%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20website%20narendramodi.in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fcentral-finance-commission-should-revise-the-norms-for-allocation-of-funds-to-states-shri-modi-5665%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equotes%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20objective%20parameters%20are%20followed%20for%20allocating%20funds%20to%20states%20for%20implementation%20of%20central%20government%20sponsored%20schemes%2C%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20injustice%20to%20certain%20states%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20the%20present%20approach%20of%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20favours%20the%20states%20with%20poor%20fiscal%20discipline%20while%20leaving%20the%20states%20with%20higher%20growth%20rate%20disappointed.%20Mr.%20Modi%20said%20the%20Commission%20should%20change%20its%20approach%20and%20allocate%20higher%20funds%20to%20the%20states%20that%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20national%20GDP%20with%20a%20view%20to%20give%20impetus%20to%20the%20development%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20infrastructural%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20suggested%20a%20new%20formula%20for%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20states%2C%20which%20should%20be%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9C25%25%20based%20on%20population%2C%205%25%20based%20on%20migration%2C%2010%25%20based%20on%20area%2C%2035%25%20based%20on%20the%20fiscal%20capacity%20distance%2C%205%25%20based%20on%20state%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20in%20national%20economy%20and%2020%25%20based%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20fiscal%20discipline.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20in%20October%202013%2C%20in%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20the%20then%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20Modi%20demanded%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmodi-anger-with-centre-justified-bjp%2Farticleshow%2F3124848.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Central%20government%20should%20provide%2050%25%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20its%20tax%20revenues%20to%20the%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWas%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20trying%20to%20break%20the%20country%20as%20a%20chief%20minister%3F%20Did%20the%20poorer%20states%20not%20need%20the%20help%20of%20their%20richer%20counterparts%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20worth%20pondering%20over%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20has%20fiercely%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20for%20protesting%20to%20secure%20its%20fiscal%20rights.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707490796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18121214%2FGDpRC6VakAAZMy8.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-convenient-doublespeak-of-modi-over-centres-fiscal-injustice-towards-states%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20as%20the%20Gujarat%20chief%20minister%20before%202014%20had%20been%20the%20most%20vocal%20proponent%20of%20a%20fair%20devolution%20of%20taxes%2C%20and%20frequently%20attacked%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance-led%20Centre%20for%20denying%20Gujarat%20its%20fiscal%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-convenient-doublespeak-of-modi-over-centres-fiscal-injustice-towards-states%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210-Year%20Jail%2C%20Rs%201%20Crore%20Fine%3A%20Anti-Cheating%20Law%20Comes%20Hard%20On%20Malpractices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20move%20to%20ensure%20fair%20play%20in%20competitive%20exams%2C%20Parliament%20passed%20a%20bill%20on%20Friday%20introducing%20strict%20penalties%20for%20malpractices.%20The%20Public%20Examinations%20(Prevention%20of%20Unfair%20Means)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20allows%20for%20a%20maximum%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20hefty%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20those%20found%20guilty%20of%20cheating%20or%20aiding%20in%20any%20form%20of%20irregularity.%20The%20bill%20sailed%20through%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20with%20a%20voice%20vote%2C%20following%20its%20earlier%20approval%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20February%206th.%20Notably%2C%20amendments%20proposed%20by%20opposition%20members%20were%20rejected%20during%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20law%20sends%20a%20strong%20message%20against%20exam%20malpractices%2C%20aiming%20to%20level%20the%20playing%20field%20and%20ensure%20fair%20competition%20for%20all%20aspirants%20in%20crucial%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20aims%20to%20address%20dishonest%20actions%20and%20irregularities%20in%20competitive%20exams%20by%20imposing%20strict%20penalties.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20bill%20suggests%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20national%20technical%20committee%20on%20public%20examinations%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20enhancing%20the%20security%20of%20computerized%20examination%20procedures.%20This%20committee%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20providing%20recommendations%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStiff%20Penalties%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20bill%20prescribes%20a%20maximum%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20crore%20for%20those%20found%20guilty%20of%20cheating%20or%20aiding%20in%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETargets%20Organised%20Cheating%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20specifically%20targets%20individuals%20and%20institutions%20involved%20in%20organized%20cheating%20activities%2C%20like%20leaking%20question%20papers%20or%20tampering%20with%20answer%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtects%20Meritocracy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20aim%20is%20to%20deter%20unfair%20practices%20that%20undermine%20merit-based%20selection%20in%20competitive%20exams%2C%20ensuring%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20aspirants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20Status%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassed%20by%20both%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAwaiting%20presidential%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20points%20of%20contention%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExcluding%20Students%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20subjecting%20students%20and%20candidates%20to%20penalties%20raises%20concerns%2C%20as%20Union%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjitendra-singh-students-candidates-not-under-purview-of-anti-cheating-law-minister-5005601%5C%22%3EJitendra%20Singh%20informed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on