%20Janata%20Party%20for%20creating%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20hate%20and%20communal%20violence%20that%20is%20leading%20to%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20court%20had%20slammed%20the%20state%20government%20for%20not%20complying%20with%20its%20order%20to%20depute%20an%20agency%20for%20counselling%20the%20Muslim%20boy%20and%20his%20classmates%20who%20were%20allegedly%20instructed%20by%20their%20school%20teacher%20to%20slap%20him%20for%20not%20doing%20his%20homework.%20The%20court%20had%20appointed%20TISS%20Mumbai%20to%20suggest%20the%20mode%20and%20manner%20of%20counselling%20the%20boy%20and%20his%20classmates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%206%20last%20year%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20also%20instructed%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20facilitate%20the%20admission%20of%20the%20boy%20to%20a%20private%20school.%20Tushar%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20great-grandson%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20moved%20the%20court%20seeking%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%2C%20on%20October%2030%20last%20year%2C%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20immediately%20consider%20granting%20sanction%20to%20prosecute%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707489014000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28095821%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmuslim-boy-slapping-row-case-sc-slams-up-govt-for-not-counselling-students%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20had%20earlier%20ordered%20the%20state%20government%20to%20approach%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20to%20counsel%20students.%20In%20its%20latest%20order%2C%20it%20directed%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20file%20compliance%20report%20in%20two%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmuslim-boy-slapping-row-case-sc-slams-up-govt-for-not-counsell