nt%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20accused%20by%20the%20BJP%20of%20disrespecting%20its%20own%20leader%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20has%20welcomed%20the%20announcement%20that%20the%20government%20will%20confer%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20-%20but%20not%20without%20taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20ruling%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20praised%20Rao's%20contribution%20to%20nation-building%20and%20India's%20nuclear%20programme%2C%20and%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20economic%20reforms%20were%20carried%20out%20under%20his%20government%20in%201991.%20Former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20senior%20party%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20also%20expressed%20happiness%20at%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20father%20of%20India's%20green%20revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Former%20Congress%20President%2C%20Shri%20P%20V%20Narasimha%20Rao%20has%20tremendously%20contributed%20to%20nation%20building.%20Under%20his%20government%2C%20India%20embarked%20on%20a%20transformative%20journey%20with%20a%20series%20of%20economic%20reforms%20that%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20middle%20class%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20behalf%20of%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20we%20welcome%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20being%20conferred%20to%20Shri%20P%20V%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20Dr%20M%20S%20Swaminathan.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Former%20Congress%20President%2C%20Shri%20P%20V%20Narasimha%20Rao%20has%20tremendously%20contributed%20to%20nation%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1755901051553947747%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20Mr%20Rao%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20India's%20Nuclear%20programme%20and%20his%20tenure%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20number%20of%20foreign%20policy%20achievements%2C%20including%20the%20'Look%20East'%20policy%2C%20the%20Congress%20chief%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BHis%20vital%20role%20in%20the%20prosperity%20and%20development%20of%20our%20nation%20shall%20always%20be%20cherished%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20%26quot%3Ba%20son%20of%20the%20soil%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20said%20he%20had%20helped%20strengthen%20rural%20India.%20He%20also%20praised%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20institution%20builder%20par%20excellence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20party%20applauds%20their%20vision%2C%20their%20hardwork%20and%20the%20exceptional%20legacies%20of%20these%20national%20icons%2C%20which%20the%20nation%20has%20always%20celebrated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20president%20posted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20when%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20announcements%2C%20specifically%20for%20Rao%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20them...%20why%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20former%20Union%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20welcomed%20the%20announcement%2C%20he%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20discovering%26quot%3B%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20three%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHappy%20that%20secular%2C%20socialist%20leaders%20have%20been%20awarded%20Bharat%20Ratna.%20It%20is%20gratifying%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20dis