ds%20once%20I%20had%20harvested%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20flowers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20seeds%20require%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20soil%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F245524%2Fherb-heaven-saffron-organic-farming-kashmir-mir-family-business-legacy-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20plucked%2C%20he%20advises%20setting%20up%20an%20area%20where%20you%20can%20ensure%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%202%3A%20Check%20the%20seeds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20journey%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20Gujarat%20is%20tiring%20for%20the%20seeds.%20Dormant%20during%20travel%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20attract%20moisture%2C%20which%20gets%20collected%20in%20their%20outer%20layers.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20seeds%20arrive%2C%20you%20need%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20well%20aerated%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20moisture%20or%20fungus%20will%20set%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20cautions%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F272981%2Fhow-to-grow-vegetables-in-pots-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESorting%20out%20the%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20ordeal.%20They%20need%20to%20be%20checked%20by%20hand%20and%20smelled%20to%20catch%20any%20rot%20that%20has%20set%20in.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20one%20seed%20with%20fungus%20can%20affect%20the%20whole%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStep%203%3A%20Divide%20the%20batch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESorting%20through%20the%20seeds%20leaves%20you%20with%20the%20good%20ones%20and%20the%20bad.%20You%20discard%20the%20bad%20ones%20and%20proceed%20with%20silvering%20the%20good%20ones.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20step%2C%20the%20tail-like%20portion%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20seed%20is%20cut%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C