sts%2C%20especially%20agricultural%20scientists%20who%20are%20often%20not%20in%20the%20limelight%20but%20are%20so%20important%20-%20were%20in%20the%20past%20and%20will%20be%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20award%2C%20announced%20just%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP's%20way%20of%20wooing%20the%20south%3F%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20frankly%20I'm%20not%20even%20thinking%20about%20those%20things.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20politics%20here%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20tribute%20to%20an%20individual.%20It's%20a%20tribute%20to%20my%20father%20and%20you%20know%20we%20have%20seen%20from%20childhood...%20He%20had%20an%20amazing%20ability%20-%20whether%20it%20was%20farmers%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country%20or%20whether%20it%20was%20politicians%20or%20whether%20it%20was%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20Nobel%20laureates%2C%20he%20was%20equally%20at%20home%20in%20all%20of%20the%20settings%20and%20I%20think%20it%20was%20that%20special%20gift%20he%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20the%20Padma%20awards%2C%20they%20come%20from%20all%20over%20India...%20My%20father%20never%20considered%20himself%20to%20particularly%20belong%20to%20any%20one%20state%20or%20community.%20I%20think%20he%20really%20was%20an%20Indian.%20He%20belonged%20to%20the%20Gandhian%20era.%20He%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20era%20of%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20for%20him%2C%20the%20country%20was%20above%20everything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20two%20former%20PMs%20-%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20-%20and%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Green%20Revolution%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20matter%20of%20immense%20joy%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20announced%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20for%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20and%20said%20the%20honour%20was%20being%20conferred%20on%20the%20scientist%20%26quot%3Bin%20recognition%20of%20his%20monumental%20contributions%20to%20our%20nation%20in%20agriculture%20and%20farmers'%20welfare%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F4cgvdl_soumya-swaminathan_625x300_02_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-fitting-tribute-ex-who-chief-scientist-dr-soumya-swaminathan-on-bharat-ratna-to-father-ms-swaminathan-5026058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20is%20very%20happy%20and%20delighted%20with%20the%20honour%2C%20said%20Dr%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%2C%20former%20chief%20scientist%20of%20WHO%20and%20the%20daughter%20of%20noted%20agricultural%20scientist%20MS%20Swaminathan%20who%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-fitting-tribute-ex-who-chief-scientist-dr-soumya-swaminathan-on-bharat-ratna-to-father-ms-swaminathan-5026058%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-fitting-tribute-ex-who-chief-scientist-dr-soumya-swaminathan-on-bharat-ratna-to-father-ms-swaminathan-5026058%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-fitting-tribute-ex-who-chief-scientist-dr-soumya-swaminathan-on-bharat-ratna-to-father-ms-swaminathan-5026058%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Search%20for%20runner%20and%20mum-of-three%20who%20vanished%20six%20days%20ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707484680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-samantha-murphy-victoria-police_6449609.jpg%3F20240209123645%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustralia-victoria