al%20after%20serving%20for%20a%20good%2040%20years%2C%20whereas%20women%20officers%20were%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20only%20after%2010-14%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20the%20ropes%20of%20gender%20inequality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20Garima%2C%20who%20practices%20law%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20decided%20to%20fight%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%20They%20were%20led%20by%20Rekha%20Palli%20%5Bnow%20sitting%20Judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%5D%2C%20and%20her%20competent%20team%20of%20female%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20us%2C%20she%20explains%20how%20the%20team%20fought%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295810%2Fgender-equality-at-workplace-accenture-empowers-women-for-leadership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20equality%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Garima%20%5Bcentre%5D%20fought%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sac