ity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judgment%20was%20said%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20only%20those%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20service%20or%20those%20retired%2Freleased%20officers%20who%20were%20not%20in%20service%20as%20on%2012%20March%202010%20but%20had%20filed%20writ%20petitions%20before%20their%20release%20%E2%80%93%20a%20criterion%20that%20did%20not%20match%20with%20the%20appellants%20and%20hence%20they%20were%20left%20out%20from%20the%20reinstatement%20plan%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20immediately%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20challenging%20the%20manner%20of%20implementation%20of